post_title: Partial PSA set break-HoF, SL graded 1-6-all cards all SOLD
post_content:
Available is about 25% of the t206 set and includes HoF, SL and commons in PSA slabs.  Most are in the 4-5 range but others fall on either side of that with some 1-2s and a few 6s.  Mostly common backs but there are a few Sovereign, Polar Bear and Old Mill sprinkled in there.  These are duplicates for me which is why they're available.  

I have what is available on the registry and can be found in the link below.  No prices there but I'm happy to send you a complete list of asking prices if you send me an email at [url]tbrambo@yahoo.com[/url].  Prices on the sheet are asking, are net of any fees and include shipping.

I've added a few scans but certainly not the 120 or so that are available.  

If you PM me (which is fine), I can't send you the .pdf so please email me and I'll get you the full list of what's left.

Here's the link (with scans)

[url]https://www.psacard.com/psasetregistry/baseball/t206-sets/1909-11-t206-complete-player-image-set-no-wagner-doyle-n-y-natl-plank-magie/publishedset/514650[/url]

Thanks!
Thanks for the interest!  All cards are pending sale.
